Waiting

Waiting

It is morning. I am waiting.

Why am I no good at waiting.

I want to sit, like a rock just sits, 

wait, just like a tree just waits.

But I can't.

Waiting.

Pacing.

Thinking.

Staring.

Stop pacing. Just waiting.

Do less in more time.

Waiting.